  <brief_title>First-in-Human Exploratory Single Ascending Dose of GLPG0974</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exploratory Double-blind Placebo-controlled Study for the Assessment of Pharmacokinetics (PK), Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacodynamics (PD) of Single Ascending Oral Doses of GLPG0974 in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
