  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this exploratory first-in-human study is to evaluate the amount of GLPG0974
      present in the blood (pharmacokinetics) after single oral doses of GLPG0974 given to healthy
      subjects.

      Furthermore, during the course of the study, safety and tolerability as well as the effects
      of GLPG0974 on mechanism of action-related parameters in the blood (pharmacodynamics) will be
      characterized compared to placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
